      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          Sunt suficiente 8GB RAM pentru un ultrabook business?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Pentru sarcini de baza (mail, browsing, Office), da. Dar pentru multitasking serios, cu multe taburi, aplicatii deschise sau masini virtuale, 16GB RAM face o diferenta uriasa in fluiditatea sistemului.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          Ce procesor aleg: Intel Core i5 sau i7?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Pentru majoritatea utilizatorilor de business, un i5 de generatie recenta e perfect. Un i7 este necesar daca lucrezi cu aplicatii foarte solicitante (editare video, randare 3D, baze de date mari).</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          Cat de importanta e placa video dedicata intr-un ultrabook business?
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Pentru majoritatea sarcinilor de business, placa video integrata (Intel Iris Xe, AMD Radeon Graphics) e suficienta. Doar daca lucrezi cu aplicatii grafice intensive, gaming sau design 3D, vei avea nevoie de o placa dedicata (Nvidia GeForce sau Quadro, AMD Radeon Pro).</div>
      </div>
